## 4. StateResponse (The Decision & Evidence Log)

This table is the "Why" behind a status change. It links a specific decision to a lifecycle transition.

| Column | Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `stateResponseId` | UUID/PK | Unique identifier for the decision. |
| `linkToMappingId` | UUID | Pointer to the NEW `state_current` row in the MAP. |
