| `decision` | String | e.g., "Approved", "Rejected", "Queried", "Issued". |
| `commentText` | Text | Human/Agent justification for the move. |
| `linkToRoleId` | UUID | The persona/role used to authorize this move. |
| `createdDateTime` | BigInt | Audit timestamp (Unix MS UTC). |
| `certifiedBy` | UUID | The `userId` of the actor. |

