## 5. StateTransitionRules (The Gatekeeper)

Defines "Legal Moves." Checked by the API before a new `state_current` is birthed in the MAP.

| Column | Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `ruleId` | UUID/PK | Unique rule identifier. |
| `fromState` | String | The "Starting" status string (e.g., "DRAFT"). |
| `toState` | String | The "Destination" status string (e.g., "APPROVED"). |
